{
  "chapter": "019",
  "title": "惠景间侯者年表",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "太史公读列封至便侯。"
    },
    "1.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>读诸侯封列，读到便侯的时候说：是有原因的啊！"
    },
    "1.2": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">长沙</span>王，记载于<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">令甲</span>之中，称颂他的忠诚。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "高祖异姓诸侯王。"
    },
    "2.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "从前<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">平定</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天下</span>时，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">功臣</span>中非同姓而以疆土封王的有八国。"
    },
    "2.2": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝惠帝</span>时，只有<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">长沙</span>国得以保全，传位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五世</span>，因无后嗣而绝封，始终没有过错，尽藩守之职，忠信可见。"
    },
    "2.3": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "所以其恩泽流及旁支庶子，没有战功而获封为侯的有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数人</span>。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "惠景间封侯概况。"
    },
    "3.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "从<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝惠</span>起到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝景</span>的<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五十载</span>之间，追加<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>时遗漏的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">功臣</span>，以及跟从<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">代</span>而来、<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">吴</span><span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">楚</span>之役立功、诸侯子弟亲贵、外国<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">归义</span>之人，受封者共<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">九十有余</span>人。"
    },
    "3.2": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "都列表记录始末，这些是当世<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">仁义</span>成就功业中显著的事迹。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">惠</span>帝、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景</span>帝之际，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天下</span>已经平定。 诸<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">吕</span>构祸乱政，<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">吴</span><span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">楚</span>连兵叛乱。 <span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">条侯</span>出征讨伐，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">壮武</span>侯奉迎拥立。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">薄</span>氏、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦</span>氏得沐恩泽，<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">张</span>氏、<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">赵</span>氏忠贞不二。 本家枝叶分受荫庇，肺腑骨肉尽皆归诚。 <span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">新市</span>死于王事，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">建陵</span>立下勋荣。 都得裂土分封青社，都接受天子旌旗之赐。 回顾<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">甲令</span>所录，<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">吴</span>氏便享有盛名。"
    }
  }
}